      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Week 3 of "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "link",
              "attrs": {
                "href": "https://advisoryhour.substack.com",
                "target": "_blank",
                "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow",
                "class": null
              }
            }
          ],
          "text": "Summer into AI 2026"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " hosted by "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "link",
              "attrs": {
                "href": "https://advisoryhour.substack.com",
                "target": "_blank",
                "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow",
                "class": null
              }
            }
          ],
          "text": "@advisoryhour"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " — theme: Data.Punk."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Consumer Financial Protection Bureau has collected hundreds of thousands of complaints from Americans about their banks, credit card companies, and fintechs. Every complaint is public. Complaint Storm pulls up to 500 real federal complaints about any financial company, turns each one into a physics particle, and then makes AI argue both sides of the evidence simultaneously — prosecution vs. defense, streaming live."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "How the AI works"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bullet_list",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "CFPB data layer"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " — /api/complaints hits the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau's public API (no key required). Returns up to 500 real complaints with issue type, consumer narrative, company response, and date. Computes aggregations client-side."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "Dual-prosecution SSE"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " — /api/duel sends the complaint data to Claude with a custom prompt that forces alternating "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "[P]"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " (prosecution) and "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "[D]"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " (defense) paragraphs. The server parses these markers in the stream and routes each chunk to the correct column on the frontend — so both columns type simultaneously."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "Canvas particle physics"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " — Each complaint becomes a particle with momentum, friction, and cluster gravity. Particles group around 5-8 issue-type gravity wells, trail behind themselves as they move, and flee the cursor on hover. No libraries — raw Canvas API."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "How to play"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bullet_list",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Type any financial company name and hit Search — or click one of the quick-pick chips (Wells Fargo, JPMorgan Chase, Bank of America, Coinbase, Equifax)"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Watch up to 500 real federal complaints materialize as colored particles: red for fraud, orange for billing, cyan for credit reporting, purple for loans. The particle storm clusters by issue type"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Hover a cluster to see individual complaint details. The right panel streams a live ticker of recent complaint narratives"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Click "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "Initiate Duel"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " — Claude simultaneously argues The Prosecution (red column) and The Defense (blue column) using the actual complaint data, then delivers a Verdict with 3 consumer action items."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
